'''Taint''' was a [[Force power/Legends|Force power]] that allowed a Force-user to taint an object or person, such as it was the case after, while seeking revenge, [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Grand Master/Legends|Grand Master]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] [[Duel on Terephon|fought]] [[Dark Lord of the Sith/Legends|Dark Lady of the Sith]] [[Lumiya]] and [[Sai cha/Legends|beheaded her]] leading to the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]], thus causing Force-users connected to the [[Light side of the Force/Legends|light side]] to feel great pain.<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Invincible">''[[Legacy of the Force: Invincible]]''</ref> The object or person would radiate the dark side to any [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]]. If the being was neither of the dark side, or light side, and they came into contact with the object then it would cause them to suffer a stun effect. Because of the nature of this power, it would cause beings to be seduced by the dark side.

==Usage==
This power could be used not just to confound lightsiders, but also to infest places to make it seem like a user was somewhere since departed.<ref>''[[Darth Bane: Dynasty of Evil]]''</ref>

